  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1053">
<l>karappilā neñciṟ kaṭaṉaṟivār muṉṉiṉ</l>
<l>ṟirappumō rēe ruṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is even a beauty in standing before and begging of those who are liberal in their gifts and understand their duty (to beggars).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
